-- U.S. bank shares plummet
-- 
-- Thu Nov 20, 2008 11:11am EST
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2008/11/20/us-banks-shares-idUSTRE4AJ5QP20081120

 

 (Reuters) - Shares of U.S. banks fell on Thursday. Highlights: 

 * Citigroup Inc ( C.N ) shares fall as much as 25.5 percent to $4.77 * Bank of America Corp ( BAC.N ) shares fall as much as 10.6 percent to $11.68 * JPMorgan Chase & Co ( JPM.N ) shares fall as much as 18.5 percent to $23.21 * S&P financials index .GSPF falls as much as 8.5 percent * Goldman Sachs Group Inc ( GS.N ) shares fall as much as 11.1 percent to $49.00 * Morgan Stanley ( MS.N ) shares fall as much as 12.2 percent to $9.00